Type: Package
Package: stabilityselectr
Title: R Package to Perform Stability and Cluster Selection
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Stu",
           family = "Field",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "stu.g.field@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1024-5859"))
    )
Description: The Stability Selection package performs stability
    selection with a variety of kernels provided by the 'glmnet' package,
    and provides simple tools for plotting and extracting selected
    features. There is additional functionality designed to facilitate 
    various forms of permutation clustering analyses.
